      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defies its age, maintained to the highest possible standards. This car is in showroom condition, having spent its life in a climate-controlled garage under a custom cover. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster, free from any swirls, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery is supple and shows zero signs of wear, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a complete, documented history included. The engine bay is immaculate, and the driving experience is as tight and responsive as the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a specimen that is virtually indistinguishable from new.",
